name: Where it all Started
description:
the #Blinddate Valentine's collab event all started with 75 brave Tezos NFT artist putting their name in a hat, which was put on this wheel and was spun to match up the artist in our first ever Blinddate event, some of those matches were a great success, which will hopefully lead to future collaborations!  Some were a flop, a few were re-matched in the last 48 hours to do a speed date!

Check out the finished projects at  https://nftbiker.xyz/event/valentine?sort=popularity

When sold on secondary this account will receive 25% commission to support future events, if the events stop at some point in the future the Tezos collected to support emerging artist in the TEZOS blockchain community.
